des: Welcome to the LSUS Community Flash Briefing—a monthly roundup created for MCOM 215! Catch highlights of campus events, student activities, and athletic matchups, all in one quick, engaging update. Please note, this is a trial project and not an official LSUS account. Stay tuned for a fresh perspective on campus each month!
